<item>
            <title>[LU-8002] update mkfs.lustre.8 to provide usage for multiple mgsnode options.</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8002</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If the primary node is 10.102.133.18 and the secondary is 10.102.133.19&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;mkfs.lustre --mdt --fsname=IRN1_C --servicenode=10.102.133.19@tcp --servicenode=10.102.133.18@tcp --mgsnode=10.102.133.19@tcp --mgsnode=10.102.133.18@tcp --index=0 /dev/mapper/mpathb
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Will fail on first time mount&lt;br/&gt;
This:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;mkfs.lustre --mdt --fsname=IRN1_C --servicenode=10.102.133.19@tcp --servicenode=10.102.133.18@tcp --mgsnode=10.102.133.18@tcp --mgsnode=10.102.133.19@tcp --index=0 /dev/mapper/mpathb
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;will work.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This usage requirements must be recorded in mkfs.lustre.8&lt;/p&gt;</description>
